channel.title: Fagex.net Drop party! You are all invited!
channel.description:
Well fagex is having a drop party and I would personally like to extend the invitation to you! So all people who are interested, the party is starting VERY shortly! There should be about 10M worth of stuff dropped from the staff and you are more than welcome to drop stuff yourself! [img]http://sigshack.globalsigalliance.com/uploads/4a3c6bad5a.gif[/img] it
THE World will Be : 52 ****************
----------------------------------------------------------------------------- The After Pk party ----------------------------------------------------------------------------- All are Welcome to join me for some Funning Pking f2p we well be going to a multi combat zone and will kill any one outside fagex if u wish to join Just follow me after the party
FireFly
